title: The Big Cheese Poutinerie
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has two vegan poutine made with vegan Daiya cheese and mushroom gravy. Can get traditional poutine with vegan cheese and gravy, or loaded veggie poutine with sauteed mushroom, caramelized onion, roasted peppers, sweet baby peas. Note: the vegan poutine option is only listed on the take-out menu.
